1
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:45,719
Mr. Zhang, what took you so long?

2
00:00:46,159 --> 00:00:47,159
I've been waiting for you forever.

3
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,119
This one.

4
00:00:51,359 --> 00:00:52,640
Okay, okay.

5
00:01:13,159 --> 00:01:14,560
Rewrite Destiny

6
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:16,920
I am the master of my fate.

7
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,120
Not heaven.

8
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:31,560
Sir, come in.

9
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:32,519
Okay.

10
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,560
I've thought it through.

11
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,560
I can agree to work with you.

12
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,319
But let me be clear again.

13
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,359
I must have

14
00:01:43,359 --> 00:01:45,400
actual control over my project.

15
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:47,599
Fine.

16
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:48,519
Anyway, I have absolutely

17
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:50,159
no interest in your project.

18
00:01:51,159 --> 00:01:52,280
As long as it makes me money.

19
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:52,959
And

20
00:01:53,439 --> 00:01:56,319
I personally want 100,000 yuan as payment.

21
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,400
I want it now.

22
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,200
You can barely even bend over,

23
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,240
and you still want money?

24
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,439
I'm selling my product,

25
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,639
not my dignity.

26
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,840
I've made myself perfectly clear.

27
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,400
Take it or leave it.

28
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:16,840
I won't stiff you.

29
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,800
It's just 100,000 yuan.

30
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:21,159
I spend more than that on my car in a month.

31
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:22,639
You sign, I pay.

32
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,360
There are no eternal enemies.

33
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:40,080
Only eternal interests.

34
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:41,560
Never thought after all these years,

35
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,120
we'd be in the same boat again.

36
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,800
You and I will never be in the same boat.

37
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:52,840
Then

38
00:02:54,719 --> 00:02:57,120
someone's going overboard first.

39
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,400
Mom!

40
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:08,599
We'll do the checkup first today.

41
00:03:09,039 --> 00:03:10,960
If there's nothing seriously wrong,

42
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,439
we'll do the surgery tomorrow.

43
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,159
Anyone home?

44
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:22,280
Who are you looking for?

45
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,599
Which one of you is Zhang Xiaobei?

46
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:24,639
I am.

47
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:26,759
I'm Prosperity Group's legal counsel.

48
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:28,560
You are accused of Misappropriation of company funds.

49
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,319
The Group sent me to inform you

50
00:03:30,319 --> 00:03:31,840
that if you don't return it in time,

51
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,360
we'll call the police and sue you.

52
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:35,560
You'll definitely face Imprisonment.

53
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,319
Misappropriation of company funds?

54
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,879
I'm not even your employee.

55
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:39,759
How could I?

56
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:46,280
Sheng Yuanzhou gave me that money!

57
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:48,039
That was my pay.

58
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:48,759
You've got it wrong.

59
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:50,400
Looks like you'll deny it to the bitter end.

60
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:53,520
What are you doing?

61
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:55,039
Son, Xiaobei!

62
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,879
Regarding the AI program Prosperity Group

63
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:58,400
authorized you to develop,

64
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:00,039
there are Supplemental Agreements you must sign.

65
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,479
The control and ownership of my project

66
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:05,680
will all belong to you.

67
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,199
This is daylight robbery!

68
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,319
I will never sign this.

69
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:11,360
Honey...

70
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,840
We'll pay it back.

71
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:14,400
I'm not getting the treatment.

72
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,919
Sir, ma'am,

73
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,600
if he insists on not signing,

74
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,720
then I'll have to send your son to jail.

75
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,240
Take him.

76
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,000
Wait!

77
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,480
Son, just sign it.

78
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,600
We can't afford to cross them.

79
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,000
Mom!

80
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:29,879
Honey!

81
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:30,639
Mom!

82
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,199
Sheng Yuanzhou, you Bastard!

83
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:40,920
You lied to me!

84
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,319
You lied to me! You lied to me!

85
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:44,800
Lie to you?

86
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,720
You stole my project!

87
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,199
It's in black and white in the contract.

88
00:04:48,199 --> 00:04:49,040
What did I lie to you about?

89
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,399
Quit putting on an act.

90
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,959
You tampered with that 100,000 yuan

91
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:52,680
you gave me.

92
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,240
You framed me for embezzling company funds!

93
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,079
And you hired a lawyer to force me to sign!

94
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:57,720
So you could take my program for yourself!

95
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,519
You...

96
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:03,240
So what?

97
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:04,720
Zhang Xiaobei.

98
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:07,079
You think you're the only one who can code?

99
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:08,040
Let me tell you.

100
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:11,000
With money, I can hire coders anywhere.

101
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,240
You want to negotiate with me?

102
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:13,480
You're not worthy.

103
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,360
Don't go!

104
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,759
Don't go! Don't go!

105
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:19,279
Don't go!

106
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:20,360
Let go of me!

107
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,759
Get off me!

108
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:43,439
Si Qi!

109
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:46,920
Si Qi!

110
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,920
Si Qi, why are you with him?

111
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,279
Tell him.

112
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,600
Zhang Xiaobei,

113
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,279
we're over.

114
00:05:59,519 --> 00:06:01,240
The one I'm marrying now is Sheng Yuanzhou.

115
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,560
He and I belong in the same world.

116
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:05,079
And you, right now,

117
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,319
have nothing.

118
00:06:10,879 --> 00:06:11,639
You heard her.

119
00:06:12,399 --> 00:06:13,480
I expect you to stop

120
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,720
harassing me and my fiancée.

121
00:06:27,319 --> 00:06:28,079
Get off me!

122
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,839
Get off me! I'm not leaving!

123
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,279
Get off me!

124
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,680
Has your money still not come through?

125
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:27,480
Xiaobei, why aren't you answering?

126
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,720
Xiaobei, Xiaobei...

127
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,519
Answer the phone! Pick up!

128
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,600
Meeting me privately won't change anything.

129
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,240
I'm telling you.

130
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,480
The AI program project is a done deal.

131
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,439
Neither of us can change that.

132
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,480
Sheng Yuanzhou.

133
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,759
You want the project?

134
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,319
I can give it to you.

135
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:50,000
But you have to give me that 100,000 yuan.

136
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,560
That's my mom's life-saving money.

137
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,759
If you really want money, keep quiet.

138
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,439
Maybe when I'm in a good mood someday,

139
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:57,959
I might just give it to you.

140
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,879
Sheng Yuanzhou.

141
00:08:01,199 --> 00:08:02,480
Why are you doing this to me?

142
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,360
Ever since we were in school,

143
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,639
you've been targeting me at every turn.

144
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:05,680
If back then you hadn't

145
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,399
framed me for taking money to write papers,

146
00:08:07,399 --> 00:08:08,920
I wouldn't have been expelled.

147
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,360
Don't bring up the past with me.

148
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,519
If you'd just played along back then

149
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:13,360
and sold me the paper,

150
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,319
my dad wouldn't have found out,

151
00:08:14,319 --> 00:08:15,079
and it wouldn't have turned into that mess.

152
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,160
Bottom line, you brought it on yourself.

153
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:21,920
I brought it on myself?

154
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,399
You think having a little dirty money

155
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,720
means you can do whatever you want?

156
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,720
So that's why you asked me out here.

157
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,560
Tell me,

158
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:33,360
if this recording goes online,

159
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:35,200
what happens to your family's stock price?

160
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,720
What will your dad do to you?

161
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:43,679
Don't you just want money?

162
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,679
I can give it to you.

163
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:45,399
Delete it.

164
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:48,399
No. I'm selling it to the media.

165
00:08:48,559 --> 00:08:49,360
Yeah, I need money,

166
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,919
but I want you ruined even more.

167
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,600
Give it to me.

168
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,120
If you dare release it,

169
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,919
you're finished too.

170
00:08:58,919 --> 00:09:00,240
You'll end up like your sister.

171
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:03,960
What did you say?

172
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,639
If your sister had listened to me back then,

173
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,240
she wouldn't have ended up like this.

174
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,639
Make yourself clear.

175
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,120
What the hell did you do to my sister?

176
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:28,919
Let go of me!

177
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,440
What right did you have to treat her like that?

178
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:31,799
Let go of me!

179
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:32,919
Why did you do that to my sister?

180
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,080
It wasn't me.

181
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:52,720
Zhang Xiaobei.

182
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:01,759
Tell me!

183
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:04,960
Who was it that killed my sister?

184
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:09,879
Your mistake is being afraid,

185
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:10,840
always shrinking back.

186
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:12,279
Don't waste your energy

187
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:14,159
on a worthless life like that.

188
00:10:14,519 --> 00:10:16,480
Put away that useless sympathy.

189
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,559
Do what you're supposed to do.

190
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,679
Who was it?

191
00:10:24,639 --> 00:10:25,919
Stop asking.

192
00:10:25,919 --> 00:10:27,279
Tell me!

193
00:10:48,159 --> 00:10:49,000
Zhang Xiaobei.

194
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,919
We're over.

195
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:53,200
The one I'm marrying now is Sheng Yuanzhou.

196
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,279
He and I belong in the same world.

197
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,679
Exchange Fates.

198
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,799
Sheng Yuanzhou!

199
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,200
I won't let you get away with this!

200
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:22,879
I don't want another life.

201
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:31,200
I'm going to use your identity

202
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:34,240
and repay the humiliation you put my family through

203
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,720
a hundred times over.

204
00:11:59,399 --> 00:12:00,240
What are you doing?

205
00:12:19,399 --> 00:12:22,399
This is Sheng Yuanzhou's father, Sheng Shizhong.

206
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:24,480
Dad!

207
00:12:26,039 --> 00:12:26,799
What?

208
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:29,679
Let go!

209
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,000
I'm sorry!

210
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:57,600
I'm sorry.

211
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,039
I'm sorry.

212
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,000
Sheng Yuanzhou!

213
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,679
What did you do to Zhang Xiaobei?

214
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,320
Sheng Yuanzhou!

215
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:39,679
I'm Sheng Yuanzhou now.

